Title : List of indoor arenas in Belgium
Text : {{Unreferenced|date=May 2014}}
The following is a '''list of indoor arenas in [[Belgium]]''', ordered by capacity.
The venues are by their final capacity after construction for seating-only events. There is more capacity if standing room is included (e.g. for concerts).

==Current arenas==

